Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charm up my Mai dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.23,0:00:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看电视的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保持房间明亮  并远离电视收看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要向大家征集话剧演什么内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不允许让自己当主演
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐班里其他同学出演的剧情什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们会总结大家的意见进行编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样分配好像比较能让大家认同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.06,0:02:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞  小{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}紬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在考虑咖啡厅的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.72,0:02:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（传说之树）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.32,0:02:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  对学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花井学长…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:03:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…八云同学  其实我也对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…伪装的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.23,0:03:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是  播磨拳儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花井…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没…没什么没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道  肯定是谁的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的联想到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  重振精神  看下一个  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一条  三原  你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:04:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这水平还想成为未来的明星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是  对不起  月[哔－]老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了要称呼我为[哔－]！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说几遍才懂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角小美琴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们并无恶意  原谅她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛宝石一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,level  D
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(主角  小美琴专用)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周防小姐  你的身材…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌喉…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有周防小姐你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（吞口水…）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行得怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不给我看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精彩的东西当然要留到最后再看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这到底是谁写的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}冴{\r}吧  这种恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  她就是喜欢这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看下一个吧  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  给我一碗阳春面…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是泽近集团的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经是过去的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司倒闭了  现在只能过着贫困潦倒的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们用强硬的手段让不少人流泪过吧  嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这家店也差点被害垮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷的辛苦  你稍微感受到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上还有着靠白饭和柴鱼过活的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.69,0:06:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情节展开和第一个故事很像哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这是播磨写的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概他觉得只要变装成别人就表示自己不是主角了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:28.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像播磨的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.38,0:06:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来播磨写了这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是文化祭  又写得挺好  不用顾虑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴  我有点事先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着下一个  下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}舞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时是一个普通的高中一年级女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  其实我有不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charm up my Mai dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小舞你还很喜欢这类梦幻的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  明天再继续考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总结起来还真够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有擅长这方面的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野同学  你还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高野同学你很喜欢看书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级投入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种沉着冷静  正是所谓的才貌双全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  交给高野同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.34,0:07:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  高野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.59,0:07:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试着写一下话剧的剧本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  应该说是非高野同学不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就接受了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得倒轻松…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长这个的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜  你太过严谨了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放松过头了  什么时候变成这样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没有资格说别人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小晶你真会皮笑肉不笑哎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像耍帅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧  看得出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是昨天和今天收集的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按高野同学的喜好写剧本就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某个地方  有个十分冷面无情的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然成绩不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但性格古怪又爱欺负人  是个讨人厌的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这个女孩有一个专长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢看书  也喜欢写书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩在文化祭上写了话剧的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微帮上了大家一点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个字…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烂的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  播磨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么阳春面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.18,0:09:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有体会到贫穷的辛苦真不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（续三匹斩  本节目为XX年X月X日放映之作）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  明天要住在学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为我们班文化祭准备得乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意播磨的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就交给姐姐我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱了～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…到底是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所～以～嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨喜欢的东西啦  喜欢的女孩类型啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你帮我问问啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去问的话他肯定会起疑心  爱理你去就不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打·死·我也不干！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那么讨厌播磨他吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底为什么突然要问他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是八云想知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子太内向是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点上有无敌舰队血统的爱理你一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  拜托你啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂  胡子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我在做咖啡厅菜单的问卷调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请问一下你喜…喜好的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行  不愧是爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢会做菜的女孩  yes or no？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟菜单没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太紧张了  爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NO  只要有爱  做泡面也OK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还很平常的回答了～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼光还是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那进入下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅长运动和不擅长运动的女孩  你喜欢哪一种？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒无所谓的  不过不会游泳的还是蛮可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下  下一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡子…播磨同学你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么发型的女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全跟菜单无关了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太紧张了啊  爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲在那边那个人是小满？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道我的喜好么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是你所具有的一切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  明摆着嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是把头发绑在两边的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（把我的心意传达出去吧！）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在听吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…认真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也说过没有交往对象  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  你忘了带换洗的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  八云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  去澡堂咧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生只是在隔壁洗澡而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本看不到人影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这里的的确确…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个天堂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你们没听说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快脱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  我已经看习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候如果我的发型不一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又会怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  一条身材好好哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦～不错的身材不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到了这里了还这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么大家一起进去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  1  2  上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真舒服啊  泡澡果然很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女…女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借用下洗发水吗  吉田山同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小可怜  来互相擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.98,0:14:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}小可怜  先帮我擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.26,0:14:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  感觉什么不好的事情就都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个那个  泽近同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得不应该在这种情况下问你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是正在和播磨交往呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也一直很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  告诉我们吧  泽近同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  一直在等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.43,0:15:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  都等的不耐烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我们两个人的三块塌塌米的小房间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你住在这么小的房子里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我再赚些钱就立刻搬家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真笨啊  为了等我弄得头发这么冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来为你把它弄暖和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  播磨大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生真吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得呢  你们两个的感情真是很不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  泽近同学和播磨同学说话的时候也非常的自然哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  OK了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:16:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…这样啊  我和胡子在别人眼里是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  和他在一起交谈时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有什么奇怪的顾虑和虚伪的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说真的  我自己也很惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨他  让我觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌把金发绑在两边的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊  完全不明白你说的什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…恨到想杀死他！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱理  你先出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经那么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有吃的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  女生们就做些饭团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  奈良
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完成了  泳装相扑用的丁字泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:16:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  做好了做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  怎么每一盘都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  这是我们这些做饭团的女生特意分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:11.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了后  来猜一下是谁做的饭团～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下子可麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃泽近同学的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌丸同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？  这是我做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结城同学做的啊  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.55,0:17:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我找到小满做的饭团然后说「好吃」的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满的饭团…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的  大概只有我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于味道到底怎么样  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:52.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经做好觉悟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居…居然超出了我的想象…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果这是你做出的饭团的味道的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就很幸福了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  小满！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.54,0:18:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟…糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赶快换换口味才行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭团的样子有些个性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个时候已经没有选择的余地了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难·吃！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可能  真不可置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎么做出这种东西的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能够超越小满  真让人不敢相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  原来小满的料理不是最差的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.14,0:19:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才…真是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话  能不能吃掉这些呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则不好收拾了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  没人要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道第一次吃的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  不要太勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…总算吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了  意识模糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不找点东西换下口味的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播磨！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fnDFMaruGothic-Md\fs27}塚{\r}本！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:55.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为这么努力的播磨你  特地带吃的来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来的真是时候  不愧是小满
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:19:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.08,0:20:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  全部都给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:35.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小满…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是手艺最差的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  周防
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也辛苦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了这么多事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.11,0:20:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能恢复起精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.82,0:20:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我知道了八云和播磨之间的事是误会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  你好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你又如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么…从那之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:17.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  总之这种事情就是突然发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心  慢慢等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们就来比比看谁先找到心上人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就慢慢比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是漫画能出版的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要向小满告白！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家  看着这边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.24,0:22:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茄～子～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:13.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天终于到文化祭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.14,0:23:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文化祭正式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们2-C全力以赴…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.24,0:23:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？茶道部也是开咖啡厅？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  School Rumble二学期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.11,0:23:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫画是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕也是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——八云在哪里啊？！
