Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:24:00.00,end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}{\pos(258,290)}漫画是文化
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:24:00.00,end,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}{\pos(310,357)}蛋糕也是文化
